        "kind": "agentTurn",
        "message": "检查 memory/pending/ 下是否已有昨天的 Garmin 数据文件（文件名含 Garmin- 加昨天日期）。\n\n如果已有：直接退出，不做任何操作，不发任何消息。\n如果没有：说明昨晚 23:59 的抓取失败了，立即补抓：\n  TODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\n  YESTERDAY=$(date -v-1d +%Y-%m-%d 2>/dev/null || date -d yesterday +%Y-%m-%d)\n  gccli activities --date $YESTERDAY --json > memory/pending/Garmin-$YESTERDAY.json\n  gccli steps --date $YESTERDAY --json >> memory/pending/Garmin-$YESTERDAY.json\n  gccli health sleep --date $YESTERDAY --json >> memory/pending/Garmin-$YESTERDAY.json\n  gccli heartrate --date $YESTERDAY --json >> memory/pending/Garmin-$YESTERDAY.json\n补抓完成后静默，不发消息。",
        "timeoutSeconds": 300
      },
      "delivery": {
        "mode": "none",
        "channel": "feishu",
        "to": "ou_aaf284a8365c85e8b792bb77b9bc8d59",
        "accountId": "jirou",
        "bestEffort": true
      },
      "failureAlert": {
        "after": 3,
        "channel": "feishu",
        "to": "ou_aaf284a8365c85e8b792bb77b9bc8d59",
        "accountId": "jirou",
        "cooldownMs": 3600000
